      <data key="d1">occupation</data>
      <data key="d2">25-1071.00</data>
      <data key="d3">Teach courses in health specialties, in fields such as dentistry, laboratory technology, medicine, pharmacy, public health, therapy, and veterinary medicine.</data>
      <data key="d4">onet</data>
