      <data key="d1">occupation</data>
      <data key="d2">25-1072.00</data>
      <data key="d3">Demonstrate and teach patient care in classroom and clinical units to nursing students. Includes both teachers primarily engaged in teaching and those who do a combination of teaching and research.</data>
