      <data key="d1">occupation</data>
      <data key="d2">25-1081.00</data>
      <data key="d3">Teach courses pertaining to education, such as counseling, curriculum, guidance, instruction, teacher education, and teaching English as a second language. Includes both teachers primarily engaged in teaching and those who do a combination of teaching and research.</data>
      <data key="d4">onet</data>
