      <data key="d1">occupation</data>
      <data key="d2">25-1123.00</data>
      <data key="d3">Teach courses in English language and literature, including linguistics and comparative literature. Includes both teachers primarily engaged in teaching and those who do a combination of teaching and research.</data>
