      <data key="d2">25-1124.00</data>
      <data key="d3">Teach languages and literature courses in languages other than English. Includes teachers of American Sign Language (ASL). Includes both teachers primarily engaged in teaching and those who do a combination of teaching and research.</data>
      <data key="d4">onet</data>
